net.minecraftforge.debug.gameplay

Class GiveItemToPlayerTest

  • java.lang.Object
    • net.minecraftforge.debug.gameplay.GiveItemToPlayerTest

  • public class GiveItemToPlayerTest
extends java.lang.Object
    A mod to test that ItemHandlerHelper.giveItemToPlayer works. More specifically, that all players, including the one receiving the item, can hear the pickup sound when it happens. This mod makes it so when you right click the air with a piece of dirt in your hand, you get another piece of dirt. It's not a dupe glitch...it's a dupe "feature"...
